1. Build image

docker build -t <repo> <dir>

DockerFile:
<ENTRYPOINT>
<CMD> Para to <ENTRYPOINT>


2. Rename Image
docker tag ...


3. Detailed Manual

https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/


4. Let docker to use USB device:

docker run -t -i --privileged -v /dev/bus/usb:/dev/bus/usb ubuntu bash

docker run -t -i --device=/dev/ttyUSB0 ubuntu bash

---------------------------------------------------------------
LXC

1. lxc-create

directory related: 
/var/lib/lxc  -- store the lxc container instance
/usr/share/lxc/ -- most configuration files as well the template
 MOST IMPORTANT: /usr/share/lxc/templates/lxc-ubuntu
 
 /var/cache/lxc --- the cached download package




